<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Correo con Bootstrap</title>
    <!-- Incluye Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
            padding-top: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 90px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .header h1 {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin: 0;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .content {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .content p {
            margin: 0 0 10px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .ignore {
            color: #747474;
            font-size: 14px;
            padding-top: 15px;
        }

        img {
            width: 200px;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 10px;
            display: block;
            margin: auto;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .footer p {
            color: #999;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin: 0;
        }

         .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 15px;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 17px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 0 10px;
        }

        .table th,
        .table td {
            padding: 8px;
            vertical-align: top;
            border-top: 1px solid #dee2e6;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="cover">
            <img src="cid:coverLogo" alt="">
        </div>
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Â¡Hola, maravilloso Admin!</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>El usuario {{firstName}} {{lastName}} acaba de ingresar los datos para solicitar el modo conductor. <br>Por favor revisa bien los datos del RUNT antes de aprobar.</p>
            <table class="table">
                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <th scope="row">User ID</th>
                        <td>{{userId}}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <th scope="row">First Name</th>
                        <td>{{firstName}}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <th scope="row">Last Name</th>
                        <td>{{lastName}}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <th scope="row">Gender</th>
                        <td>{{gender}}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <th scope="row">Phone Number</th>
                        <td>{{phoneNumber}}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <th scope="row">Email</th>
                        <td>{{email}}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <th scope="row">Carrer</th>
                        <td>{{carrer}}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <th scope="row">Document Type</th>
                        <td>{{documentType}}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <th scope="row">Document Number</th>
                        <td>{{documentNumber}}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <th scope="row">Brand</th>
                        <td>{{brand}}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <th scope="row">Model</th>
                        <td>{{model}}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <th scope="row">Line</th>
                        <td>{{line}}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <th scope="row">Plate</th>
                        <td>{{plate}}</td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
            <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
                <a href="https://www.runt.com.co/consultaCiudadana/#/consultaVehiculo" class="button">Verificar RUNT</a>
                <a href={{changeRolUrl}} class="button">Habilitar modo conductor</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Cordialmente,</p>
            <p>UCAR</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Incluye Bootstrap JS y dependencias de Popper.js -->
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.5.4/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>

</html>
